name: Dot - Dot x Goodnight Cody - LOVESICK

metadata.description:
LOVESICK is the first collaboration between Dot and Goodnight Cody on Sound, as well as Cody’s genesis drop on Sound. 

Dot and Cody first met in 2012 through production collective TeamSupreme, and have been friends and collaborators for over ten years. 

This drop will help to fund some much needed gear purchases for both artists: Cody needs to finally replace his 2014 MacBook, and Dot’s monitors just bit the dust after 8 years of use. 

The winner of the Golden Egg will have a special cameo* in the music video for LOVESICK, as well as receive a Dot Merch Package. 

*Other video participation options will be available if the collector wishes to remain anonymous. 

We hope you enjoy LOVESICK </3

Join the Dot Connect telegram chat: https://guild.xyz/dot-collectors 
Follow Goodnight Cody: https://www.instagram.com/goodnight_cody/
https://twitter.com/Goodnight_Cody
